<p>I grabbed lunch, I'll check snapshots when I get back to my desk. We do weekly snapshots of SCUTTLE and they should be fine, let's plan on reverting at 1700. Get lunch and come back. Be prepared to do this via cold storage to physical media, that thing sounds like it's dead as a doorknob.</p>
