<p>From: Terry Thompson [tthomp03]<br />
To: Brandon Collins [bcolli01]<br />
Cc: Maria Jones [mjones06]<br />
Sent: 20██/01/14&#160;10:44<br />
Subject: FW: SCUTTLE - Still Broken</p>
<p>I'm trying very hard not to lose my temper, but you absolutely can, and should have, as I asked you to. Where you did Image-&gt;Disk, you pick Disk-&gt;Image instead. It's literally two options down. How did you not know this?</p>
