<blockquote>
<h6 id="toc16"><span>IR#20██011300███-14, Status: <em>Reply by submitter.</em> User: <em>lrhode02</em> (<strong>IP:</strong> 10.101.25.███) Timestamp: <em>20██/01/14&#160;11:10</em></span></h6>
<p>Good morning gentlemen. I'm seeing a black screen on SCUTTLE I've never seen before. What is the status of this? LR</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<blockquote>
<h6 id="toc17"><span>IR#20██011300███-15, Status: <em>Replied.</em> User: <em>tthomp03</em> (<strong>IP:</strong> 10.101.147.███) Timestamp: <em>20██/01/14&#160;11:42</em></span></h6>
